attributes.long-description:
TEKKEN® 5: Dark Resurrection™ exploded onto the PSP® and arcade bringing added variety to the Tekken franchise. Now Tekken sets out to conquer a new platform, the PS3™ network! Fully downloadable from any connected PlayStation®3, Tekken 5 DR looks to bring the arcade action directly to PlayStation®3 homes everywhere.
The great fighting gameplay and cast of characters are all fully playable and visually customizable in this version along with the playability of Jinpachi, the formidable boss from Tekken: Dark Resurrection.
